{
  "texts": [
    "Each chatbot message was automatically converted into audio using text-to-speech technology and played when the message was displayed to the user, facilitating a more authentic interaction.",
    "The chat was initiated with a predefined user prompt introducing the chatbot: \"I'm a design bot and would love to speak with you about a design project of your choice!\"",
    "The conversations were recorded in a database.",
    "The chat logs were then summarized to create a set of design requirements for the design project.",
    "The participant would then rate these design requirements, as shown in Figure 1b."
  ]
}